item.title: Flying high with Imperial frisbee
item.author: Anthony Featherstone,Lucy J Rowlands,
item.description: Imperial’s Ultimate Frisbee club, more commonly known as the discDoctors (or dD) were in a position to bring both a women’s team and a men’s team to nationals for the first time ever, with the men having qualified in the league throughout the season, and the women finishing highly at Outdoor …
